@map
- SYS-001 | Service Overview | Clarify service scope and goals
- SYS-010 | Domain Boundaries | Separate responsibilities to reduce change impact
- SYS-020 | End-to-end Flow | Describe request-to-response path step by step
- SYS-030 | State and Event Transitions | Define business state transitions and trigger conditions
- SYS-040 | External Integrations and API Contracts | Document interface contracts to avoid integration drift
- SYS-050 | Exception and Recovery Strategy | Define retry, rollback, and compensation strategies
- SYS-060 | Operational Observability and Alerts | Define operational health metrics and alert thresholds
- SYS-070 | Abort Metrics and Guardrails | Define explicit stop conditions to prevent prolonged wrong-direction execution

